### AUTH – REGISTER USERS
### =========================================

### Register PARENT
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en

{
  "email": "parent@test.com",
  "password": "Parent123!",
  "role": "PARENT",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

